Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Wall Plank Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Use a wall for support while holding a plank position.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Frog Stand
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Balance on your hands with knees resting on your elbows.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Tuck Planche Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a tuck position while balancing on your hands.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Advanced Frog Stand
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Balance on your hands with knees off your elbows.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Straddle Planche
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a planche position with legs spread apart.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Full Planche
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a planche position with legs together.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Hollow Body Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a position with the lower back on the floor, arms, and legs lifted.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Front Lever Tuck Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a tuck position while hanging from a bar.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Front Lever Raises
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Raise your body from a dead hang into a front lever position.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Full Front Lever Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a front lever position with the body fully extended.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Archer Pull-Ups
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Pull yourself up while keeping one arm extended.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Ice Cream Makers
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Transition between a front lever and a hanging position repeatedly.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: L-Sit Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold your legs extended straight in front of you while supporting your body on parallel bars or the ground.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: One-Arm Isometric Holds
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold your body with only one arm engaged while keeping the other relaxed.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Wall Handstand Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a handstand against a wall for stability.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Freestanding Handstand
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Balance in a handstand position without support.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: One-Arm Handstand
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a handstand using only one arm.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Skin the Cat
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Rotate your body under the bar in a controlled motion.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Back Lever Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a straight body position parallel to the ground while hanging from a bar.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Human Flag Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold your body horizontal to the ground using a vertical pole.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: One-Arm Chin-Up
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Perform a chin-up using only one arm.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: One-Arm Pull-Up
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Perform a pull-up using only one arm.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Pseudo Planche Push-Ups
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Lean forward while performing push-ups to simulate a planche.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Straddle Front Lever Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a front lever with legs spread apart.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Elevated Pike Push-Ups
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Perform pike push-ups with feet elevated to build handstand push-up strength.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Tuck Handstand
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hold a handstand with legs tucked close to your chest.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Dragon Flag
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Lower and raise your body in a straight position while lying on a bench.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: German Hang Hold
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Hang upside down with arms extended behind you.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Planche Push-Ups
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Perform push-ups while maintaining a planche position.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Straight Arm Scapular Shrugs
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Engage your scapulae while hanging to build shoulder stability.

Calisthenics Skill Progressions.name: Handstand Walks
Calisthenics Skill Progressions.description: Walk forward while maintaining a handstand position.
